Package: countries
Type: Package
Title: Tidy parsing and converting of country names and codes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Edward", "Visel", 
        email = "edward.visel@gmail.com", 
        role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: countries is an alternate API to Vincent Arel-Bundock's 
    countrycodes package, supplying simple functions for parsing irregular 
    country names and converting names and codes, as well as ggplot2 scale 
    functions for presenting country names or codes in a different format from 
    that in which they are stored.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: countrycode
Suggests: ggplot2
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
